@startuml
' Task 1: MorningRoutine state machine
state Sleeping
state WakeUp
state Toilet
state Breakfast
state PrepareLunch
state Transport
state Arrive

[*] --> Sleeping
Sleeping --> WakeUp : alarmSet OR !Global_StillTired
WakeUp --> Toilet : Global_ToiletNeeded / Global_Delay += 2m
Toilet --> Breakfast : done
Breakfast --> PrepareLunch : !Global_IsHungry / Global_NeedLunch := TRUE
PrepareLunch --> Transport : lunch prepared
Transport --> Arrive : travel complete
Arrive --> [*]

note right of PrepareLunch
  Calls: AddTopping(available, currentCount)
  Uses shared `GVL` variables for availability and counts
end note
@enduml
